    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a reliable, functional daily driver rather than a showpiece. The exterior shows clear signs of use, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and typical wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it may require some routine maintenance in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a pristine model.",
