    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unparalleled caliber, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This specimen represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that reflects a history of fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. Every mechanical system operates in perfect alignment with factory specifications, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. For the discerning enthusiast who demands excellence without compromise, this offering stands as a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade vehicle of superior pedigree.",
